<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a2Aug1923"><font color="red">2 August 1923</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I shall leave Bognor either tonight or tomorrow. By the next post I hope to send on the third pattern for your loam. If all the sentences take as much trouble as these three it will be slow work. But they are only landmarks </div>
